What you need to know:  Initially, Moscow, the home to several Unesco world heritage sites and Russia’s rich architectural display was to host the Olympiad this year from July 26 to August 8Njoroge, the dreadlocked KCB Chess player had been longing to experience Moscow’s awe-inspiring beauty during Team Kenya’s visit for the championshipsAt the upcoming Games, he has set himself a target of bagging Kenya’s second ever medal at the Olympiad